  "prompt": "Abandoned? Broken hearted granny how can I stop hurting?",
  "response": "I'm sorry you're experiencing such pain. Here are some supportive suggestions:\n\n1. Emotional Support\n\u2022 Talk to trusted friends/family\n\u2022 Consider grief counseling\n\u2022 Join support groups\n\u2022 Allow yourself to feel your emotions\n\n2. Self-Care\n\u2022 Get enough sleep\n\u2022 Eat nutritious meals\n\u2022 Exercise gently\n\u2022 Practice relaxation techniques\n\u2022 Consider talking to a therapist\n\n3. Healing Strategies\n\u2022 Write in a journal\n\u2022 Practice self-compassion\n\u2022 Focus on positive memories\n\u2022 Develop new hobbies/interests\n\u2022 Stay connected with loved ones\n\n4. Professional Help\n\u2022 Seek counseling if grief feels overwhelming\n\u2022 Consider support groups for seniors\n\u2022 Talk to your doctor about managing emotional pain\n\n5. Practical Steps\n\u2022 Stay active in community\n\u2022 Volunteer\n\u2022 Connect with other family members\n\u2022 Build new social connections\n\nRemember:\n\u2022 Your feelings are valid\n\u2022 Healing takes time\n\u2022 You are loved and important\n\u2022 This pain won't last forever\n\nWould you like to discuss this more specifically?",
